title: Poland reports jump in cases amid Europe warnings
content: Cases are putting a strain on hospitals, with daily new infections exceeding 25,000 for the first time since April.

title: Sweden votes in Andersson as first female PM
content: Before MPs backed Magdalena Andersson, Sweden was the only Nordic state never to have a woman as PM.
